comments.content: What steps will reproduce the problem? 1. Put the following one line of code into a file foo.js (without the quotes): "function({}) {};" 2. Compile it with "java -jar compiler.jar --js=foo.js". What is the expected output? What do you see instead? I get an internal compiler error. The full output is included below. What version of the product are you using? On what operating system? I'm running version compiler-20091203 on OS X.
